      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先确认一下起点：SRC节点代表Education_ContentCDN作为数据源，然后流向INGEST步骤，也就是Education_ClassroomService进行内容摄取，对吗？",
