      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "清楚了，PROCESS之后接PROCVAL判断节点，输出VALID和INVALID两个分支。VALID走向CONSUME也就是Education_StudentDB进行数据消费，INVALID则走到SAFE节点，对吗？",
